Hello and Welcome to the 21st Queensland Corporate Games

The Games is set for Brisbane from May 15-17 and we are looking forward to seeing nearly 3,000 participants from over 150 organisations competing over the 3 days of competition.

Mixed Soccer is again on the Sports Programme along with Tennis, Netball, Running and 9 more sports. We are sure you will find an event you will enjoy competing in and for ease of entry, Online Accreditation is included in your Entry Fee.

Remember teams may be large or small…and anyone may be part of your team.

Please read more about or new Games Charity Legacy below…

If you would like to speak to us call 02 8354 0216 or email info@corporategames.net.au
